{
  "info": {
    "name": "Transport Passenger API - Coleccion de pruebas completa",
    "description": "Coleccion Postman generada a partir del analisis del proyecto.\n\nResumen de accesos por rol:\n- Auth: publico\n- ResourceA (Passenger): USER = GET, POST | ADMIN = CRUD completo\n- ResourceB (Trip): USER = GET | ADMIN = CRUD completo\n\nNotas:\n- El admin bootstrap del proyecto es admin@transport.local / Admin123!\n- El register siempre crea usuarios con rol USER.\n- La coleccion guarda tokenAdmin, tokenUser, passengerId y tripId en variables de coleccion.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080"
    },
    {
      "key": "tokenAdmin",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "tokenUser",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "userEmail",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "userPassword",
      "value": "Password123"
    },
    {
      "key": "userUsername",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "passengerId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "tripId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "nonExistingId",
      "value": "999999"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Endpoints publicos. No requieren token. Register crea usuarios USER.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "01 - Register USER",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
            "description": "Acceso: PUBLICO. Crea un usuario USER y retorna JWT.",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{userUsername}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{userPassword}}\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const suffix = Date.now();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"userUsername\", `user_${suffix}`);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"userEmail\", `user_${suffix}@correo.com`);",
                  "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get(\"userPassword\")) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set(\"userPassword\", \"Password123\");",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 201 Created\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test(\"Retorna token y rol USER\", function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(json.token).to.be.a(\"string\").and.not.empty;",
                  "  pm.expect(json.tokenType).to.eql(\"Bearer\");",
                  "  pm.expect(json.role).to.eql(\"USER\");",
                  "});",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"tokenUser\", json.token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "02 - Login ADMIN",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
            "description": "Acceso: PUBLICO. Login del admin bootstrap.",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@transport.local\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123!\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200 OK\", function () {",
